name: Derpy Pets NFTs: Dewey
description: Once a stray, Dewey was found in an abandoned house with several other dogs in Dallas, TX where he was severely underweight and malnurished with a bb pellet lodged in his back. Shortly after being rescued by a foster family Dewey found a permanent home with his mom and dad. Since that time Dewey has gone through an entire happy and healthy life makeover.
